Situated conveniently in the lively and well-connected area of Chandrasekharpur, Bhubaneswar, this stunning 3 BHK Residential House for rent provides the ideal combination of contemporary living and comfort. With a well-planned floor plan and a fully furnished interior, this house is perfect for families looking for a luxurious and hassle-free lifestyle.Property SpecificationsFacing towards the south direction, this brand-new house occupies a bountiful carpet area of 1,500 sqft and is located on the second floor, providing a commodious and airy living experience. The interiors with all furnishings included are of high-quality furniture, making them move-in ready. The house has 3 tastefully furnished bedrooms and 2 western-fashion bathrooms, out of which one is attached and the other is common. All the bathrooms are appointed with geysers.In addition, there are 2 balconies welcoming plenty of natural light and fresh air. Furthermore, there is also a handy shoe rack that contributes to the space organization. For a relaxed cooking experience, the kitchen comes with a granite platform, a stainless steel sink, a piped gas connection, and a separate utility area. To add finishing touches to the interiors, all the rooms are adorned with vitrified tiles for the flooring.FacilitiesThis house is planned to provide a safe and comfortable living and provides spacious open parking, 24-hour water supply and full power backup, providing uninterrupted daily life. For safety, a personal guard is present, and CCTV surveillance is provided to ensure a safe living environment for residents.LocalityStrategically located beside Bharat Petrol Pump, this house is at an advantage of being in proximity to essential services and lifestyle hubs. Schools are located within 1 km, and thus it is a suitable choice for families. Major hospitals are at a distance of 500 meters, and hence medical help is readily available. Malls and supermarkets within the same distance cater to all shopping and daily needs.The locality is well covered by public transportation, and buses and auto-rickshaws are easily available for easy travel. The railway station is just 3.5 km away, and that contributes to the property's proximity to other parts of the city. Banks and ATM centers are also within a distance of 100 meters, offering convenience in finances. The monthly maintenance is Rs 90000/-.
